The following is a list of all past and present state maintained highways and
other regionally significant highways located in the U.S. state of Nevada. All
active numbered highways (including Interstates, U.S. Routes and State Routes)
in this list are maintained by the Nevada Department of Transportation, except
for the portions of Interstate 215 and where otherwise stated.
